---
// Banner de divulgação de afiliados — exibido em posts
---
<div class="affiliate-banner" role="note" aria-label="Divulgação">
  <span class="affiliate-icon">🔗</span>
</div>
<style>
  .affiliate-banner { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.75rem; background: #fefce8; border: 1px solid #fde68a; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; border-radius: 8px; padding: 0.875rem 1rem; margin: 1rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.5; color: #92400e; }
  .affiliate-icon { font-size: 1rem; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.1rem; }
  .affiliate-banner p { margin: 0; }
  .affiliate-banner strong { font-weight: 600; }
</style>
